      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it is time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and you won't find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I just know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure, so feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
