    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is an exceptional specimen of the E46 platform, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically pristine, this vehicle has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. The exterior retains its showroom luster with zero paint correction required, while the chassis remains tight, benefitting from refreshed bushings and an uncompromised suspension geometry. This is a turn-key, investment-grade enthusiast car for the most demanding collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
