      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage since its delivery. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium upholstery shows no signs of use, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every mechanical component has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, ensuring it drives with the same precision and responsiveness as the day it left the assembly line. Complete with all original documentation, a full service history, and both sets of keys, this is a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
