      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically pristine, with a fully documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement utilizing Turner Motorsport plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a factory-spec suspension that exhibits zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior maintains its factory luster, while the engine bay is free of any weeping or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist.",
